<Layout title="UCL Quantum Society" headerShadowClass="shadow-lg shadow-primary/20">
    <main>
        <Container>
            <div class="relative pt-32">
                <div class="text-center mb-8">
                    <h1 class="text-xl font-medium text-primary">About Us</h1>
                    <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto mt-2 rounded-full"></div>
                    <p class="mt-8 text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary bg-clip-text font-light">
                        UCL Quantum Society is a platform to inspire curiosity, attract talent, and connect students with the evolving world of quantum technology and science. We collaborate with startups, research institutes, government entities and industry leaders to organise insightful events in our mission to bridge academia, technology and business. 
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-8 text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary bg-clip-text font-light">
                        Whether you're a PhD-level physicist or have never heard of a quantum computer, we're driven to provide a learning platform for everyone, cultivating a community of shared interests and unique perspectives. 
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-8 text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary bg-clip-text font-light">
